I miss you so much, Maa❤️
I wish you were here with me right now.
Some days, the weight of your absence becomes too much to bear.
I try to stay busy, surround myself with people, distract my heart with work…
But nothing really helps. Nothing fills this space you left behind.
I’m trying, Maa… I really am.
But sometimes, I just don’t know how to keep going without you.
I need you here. I need your love, your strength, your presence😔

Achievements in life are great! But true friendships in life- beyond great!!! 

The child in me comes out with these people. Love my tribe so much. 

If you ask me what are my best memories in bangalore? Each one of them will have atleast one of these characters in them. 

At the end of the day, for me, its always about people!
Aaha🙅 correction! genuine people!

[friendship, lifegoals]

Meeting @prabhudevaofficial  sir once is luck—but getting to be in his presence time and again is truly a dream come true. As a fashion designer, I live for movement, expression, and making a statement—and he’s been the epitome of that for decades. A true icon. An endless source of inspiration🙏🏻
Every time we meet, we connect, we vibe—and I walk away feeling even more driven to infuse that same magic into my own creations. His words of appreciation mean more than I can express, and they remind me exactly why I do what I do: to create, to inspire, and to leave a little sparkle behind.

Grateful. Motivated. Blessed beyond words🙏🏻

#latepost #prabhudeva #legendinspiration #dreamcometrue #icon #blessed
